headline: Capture Rolls-Royce's Record '26 Rally Through These Diversified ETFs
summary: RYCEY is up 12.9% YTD, hitting record highs in 2026; diversified ETFs like EUAD offer exposure to the rally while reducing risk from a potential pullback.
